    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "36c715c1-e297-4aaa-9171-6e163d244f29",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                    "id": "d788a60f-62b0-4654-999d-5fedbce7cf29",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "amount": "2",
                    "change": "1",
                    "notify": false
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "90937344-07bc-474e-83e6-8ec229a3dd99",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "This lesson will be about Theory and Practice of Scientific Principles. For example, there is a theory handed down from the ancient Greeks that \"Nothing comes from Nothing\" which pretty much destroys the whole \"spontaneous generation\" claptrap.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "d6993056-9d39-4d17-b625-d226f5ead45a",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Mostly, we'll concentrate upon the 'practice' part of the lesson. You will have the afternoon to test out your theories and refine your experiments.",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                    "id": "c170845d-e6a0-476d-9a71-54f68842aca1",
                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                    "actorId2": null,
                    "text": "Are there any questions?",
                    "emotion": "0",
                    "emotion2": "0",
                    "device": "0",
                    "device2": "0"
                },
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "3e71e720-9b03-44c1-af80-850d47a8f70f",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "1fecd1c3-fb89-4e9c-9ea0-f8e5dccbdfc4",
                            "text": "Say Something Flattering",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "b157af0d-d9e1-40a0-89c7-d44e3126e8b3",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Charm",
                                    "target": "64",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "810e8bc8-4c98-4777-9506-9f2a9fed932e",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f9f695e4-2c34-4018-83a2-c62c7e97e310",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "You know so much about Science.. What is your favorite scientific discovery?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d7e7fab4-def3-417c-a1fc-2fb4293ff47a",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Hmmmm... That is an interesting question... I'm rather partial to the theory that the world is just a huge Science experiment and that that we are organisms being studied. Unfortunately, that isn't a very popular theory.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cf24e85b-cfb1-4389-88f9-6f180a81123e",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "It's so hard to test such a hypothesis. I mean, am I doing something because I choose to do it or do I just think I choose to do something because the Science Experiment dictates it? Such a conundrum!",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "e3f645e5-319a-4332-a750-aaedf3600d56",
                            "text": "Ask a Clever Question",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "da1b9c97-e710-402e-b30d-f60565f592c3",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Smarts",
                                    "target": "64",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "618b1bd2-1965-4747-91f4-d8bd0be78db9",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "1",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "42ab1143-fc52-49f4-abae-9c111d1dbe45",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "What is the difference between a guess and a theory? Isn't the Scientist basically making something up?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "ad9af748-5d02-4aab-830b-be39caad8f7d",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Not at all. A theory is basically a proposed explanation about how something works. For instance, there's the theory of Gravity to explain why things fall downward when dropped. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "3fd67783-ad8d-4437-9a97-e6f30d0b1dd7",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Clearly, things fall down because \"Like attracts Like,\" and the earth is like everything else, only bigger. ",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "4",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "2624d9c8-4ea7-4488-9809-bce42d69de99",
                            "text": "Ask About Distilling Wine",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "id": "dcd28f26-dbb4-4906-8a5c-aa6883ee6d11",
                                    "type": "nodes.skillBranch",
                                    "skill": "Moxie",
                                    "target": "64",
                                    "success": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": []
                                    },
                                    "failure": {
                                        "type": "nodes.block",
                                        "nodes": [
                                            {
                                                "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                "id": "29c4ddae-4af7-44e0-bc55-6e61ea992695",
                                                "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                                "amount": "2",
                                                "change": "0",
                                                "notify": true
                                            }
                                        ]
                                    },
                                    "notify": true
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "7d668056-76ad-4041-9784-3804d4da6a8e",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "text": "So if we bring in our own wine, can we experiment today with distillating it into brandy?",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "c3d4d177-61a1-4d61-8c8e-85c1d87a7534",
                                    "actorId": "a104063f-f97b-49da-a22a-4104403e86e0",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Why would anyone want to waste their time distilling wine into brandy when they can distill a Flambe into Geek Fire? There's Science to be done!",
                                    "emotion": "4",
                                    "emotion2": "2",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0"
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "3",
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "6e607499-926c-4280-82e4-1bb5eefec944",
                            "text": "Say Nothing",
                            "nodes": [],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": 0,
                            "ExitMenu": true
                        }
                    ],
